@{b}@{u}What do you need to use NetTime?@{ub}@{uu}

 * Amiga with Kickstart 3.x (2.1?).

 * Modem connected to Amiga port.

 * EasyRexx.library Copyrighted 1994,1995 to Ketil Hunn
   (Included into archive).

 This programm is tested on A1200.

 Send all bugs to Author.

 Use that program on you own risk.
@endnode

